h3#description Description
p
	| The Menu widget is a member of the 
	a(href="/api/#{latest.version}/symbols/ch.Controllers.html") Controllers
	|  family. The navigation component works by folding the information in categories. It lets you organize large lists of links. The user select one of the folds so making focus in a part of the large list.

