h3#instance Instance component
p
	| This is the way to create a new Menu:
pre
	| var foo = $("#example").menu();
p 
	| The folds are by default closed. But you can use the 
	code selected
	|  property to open a specific children. This is the way to initialize the component with a selected item:
pre
	| var foo = $("#example").menu({"seleted": "2"});

h3#select-event "select" event
